 "\n",
 "(a) The research hypothesis is that a high BMI relates to a high blood \
pressure.\nEstimate the linear model where blood pressure is the outcome and \
BMI is the\ncovariate. Interpret the coefficients.\n(b) Calculate ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["R", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1d499e4a-e914-41eb-9297-bd8b3cf62c62"],
 " to judge the goodness of fit of the model.",
 "\n",
 Cell[BoxData["\[IndentingNewLine]"], "Input",
  CellChangeTimes->{3.9481628461414747`*^9},ExpressionUUID->
  "115879d3-e1c1-4afe-8e28-1fe35c9b1eef"]
}], "Subsubsection",
