Cell["\<\
Interpretation of coefficients: A one-unit increase in the BMI relates to a \
4.57 unit increase in the blood pressure. The model suggests a positive \
association between BMI and systolic blood pressure. It is impossible to have \
a BMI of 0; therefore, \[Alpha] cannot be interpreted meaningfully here.

Solution to (b):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.94823863127774*^9, 3.948238637092741*^9}, {
  3.9482387574080887`*^9, 
  3.948238799181909*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6ce03579-0b91-4410-9225-\
9361bf5f0784"],

