 RowBox[{"R2", "=", 
  RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948239816822847*^9, 3.9482398431601458`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[11]:=",ExpressionUUID->"6638fa30-f756-43b1-8833-79d88ab39ee5"],

Cell[BoxData["0.7568937494736889`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.948239843658556*^9, 3.9531665542587843`*^9, 
  3.95316718156142*^9, 3.9804211399998646`*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[11]=",ExpressionUUID->"24ed0fd2-8e12-d74d-a1d3-6ee203c72677"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Hence, we know that the fit of the linear regression model will be good.\n\n\
Solution to (b):\n(b) Now estimate and interpret the linear regression model \
where \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]weight\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is the outcome. \
Calculate ",
