Cell["\<\
Each centimetre difference in height therefore means a 1.109 kg difference in \
weight. It is not possible to interpret the intercept meaningfully in this \
example.

Solution to (c):
(c) Predict the weight of a student with a height 175 cm.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948240348243579*^9, 3.948240377430304*^9}, {
