Cell["\<\
This shows that the two added points shrink the estimate of beta from 1.109 \
to 0.276 . The association becomes less clear, with only 6.2% of the \
variability of the data explained by the linear regression model. This is an \
insightful example showing that least squares estimates are generally \
sensitive to outliers which can potentially affect the results .\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9482421863847923`*^9, 3.948242190631876*^9}, {
  3.9482422244305773`*^9, 3.948242249215845*^9}, {3.9482422879813232`*^9, 
  3.9482423066552963`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1077c395-900c-4f17-9c50-\
26183c4863fb"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 "3. Consider the pizza delivery data. \n(a) Read the data and fit a multiple \
linear regression model with delivery time as the outcome and temperature,  \
bill, number of ordered pizzas, and discount customer as covariates. Give a \
summary of the coefficients. \n(b) Add a quadratic polynomial of temperature \
to the model.\n(c) Estimate both ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["R", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "63bf19df-3ef7-41bd-afa7-cb07cdc7a96f"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["R", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ad5420a5-0067-441b-aab1-d266f18dde0b"],
 "adjusted for the model in (a) and the model in (b) and interpret the \
results. Plot in both cases the predicted  versus the observed values."
}], "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948163285134811*^9, 3.948163434701387*^9}, {
   3.948163750840646*^9, 3.9481637780703087`*^9}, 3.9482470245949183`*^9, {
   3.948248822583506*^9, 
   3.9482488646852903`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b1777bbe-2830-4f50-9853-\
4c07cbe3ad42"],

Cell["\<\
Solution to (a):
(a) Read the data and fit a multiple linear regression model with delivery \
time as the outcome and temperature,  bill, number of ordered pizzas, and \
discount customer as covariates. Give a summary of the coefficients.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948242420168092*^9, 3.948242434909543*^9}, {
  3.948247214054966*^9, 
  3.9482472165112953`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2476caa9-2575-4b43-8281-\
4bf39246e855"],

